userData.title: A New Movie
userData.story:
After a decade of peace in the galaxy, the
              Galactic Republic
              has struck again!
              Leia Organa
              along with the help of the
              Galactic Republic
              have set up base on
              Tatooine
              in order to devise a defensive strategy. Meanwhile
              Kylo Ren
              has launched a fleet of
              Star Destroyers to attack the planet
              Tatooine. Many hope that
              Luke Skywalker
              who has been a hero to the galaxy in the past will rise again to
              defeat the
              Galactic Republic
              once and for all.
userData.par1:
In order to seek guidance from the force
          Rey boards
          her CR90 corvette with
          her trusty droid
          Luke Skywalker and travels to the planet
          Tatooine. Upon arriving,
          she begins to meditate and is greeted by
          Force Ghost Yoda. Force Ghost
          Yoda tells
          her that
          she needs to travel to planet
          Coruscant in order to find and learn the ways of
          ancient Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn. Upon arrival to
          the planet, Rey is ambushed by
          Galactic Republic troopers. she is able to hold
          her own agaisnt the troopers at first, but begins to fail after
          reinforcements are called. Out of nowhere, ancient Jedi Master
          Qui-Gon Jinn shows up and uses the force to send a
          powerful shockwave through the ground. The troopers begin to retreat.
          The two then begin the training that was ordered by Force Ghost
          Yoda.
userData.par2:
Back on planet Tatooine, Senator
          Padmé Amidala is working with the
          Galactic Republic and plans to lead an attack on the
          Galactic Empire before they continue their conquest.
          Before anything can be done, Star Destroyers swoop
          down from the sky and begin to fire upon the city. A brigade of
          Sith troopers led by
          Sith Lord
          Darth Maul begin to invade the city and take
          several prisoners. One of these happens to be Senator
          Padmé Amidala. General
          Kit Fisto attempts to save the senator by firing
          at Sith Lord
          Dooku but succumbs to a lightsaber wound.
          All seems lost.
userData.par3:
Just as everyone is about to give up hope
          Rey shows up having completed her
          training with the ancient Jedi Master. she begins to tear down
          troopers left and right and storms into the capital building where the
          senator is being held. There, she confronts
          Darth Maul and the two engage in a lightsaber
          duel. After a long an intense struggle,
          Rey finally gains the high ground and
          strikes Darth Maul down. with this victory, the
          Galactic Empire
          retreats and the Galactic Republic gains control of
          the Galaxy once more.
          Peace
          is restored.
